IMPORTANT MEDICAL DISCLAIMER:
This software is designed for emergency blood management and educational purposes.
Always verify blood compatibility and follow proper medical protocols before 
any blood transfusion. The developers are not responsible for any medical 
decisions made using this software. Always consult qualified medical 
professionals for blood-related medical procedures.

EMERGENCY USE:
This system is intended to assist in locating blood banks and managing blood 
inventory. In actual medical emergencies, always contact local emergency 
services (911, 112, etc.) immediately.
